   <header>
      <title>Bidjat sámi boallobeavddi johtui MacOSX 10.8:s</title>
   </header>
   <body>
      <section>
         <title>Heivet Mac OS X 10.8 nu ahte lea vejolaš čállit sámegiela</title>

         <p>Jus áiggut čállit sámegiela de dárbbašat sámi boallobeavdeheivehusa.</p>

         <p>1. Raba <strong>Systemvalg…</strong></p>

         <p><img alt="Raba &quot;Systemvalg…&quot;"
         src="images/enable_sme_keyboard-systempref_menu-osx10.8-nob.png" /></p>

         <p>2. Coahkkal <strong>Språk og tekst</strong>:</p>

         <p><img alt="Systemvalg…"
         src="images/enable_sme_keyboard-systemprefs-osx10.8-nob.png" /></p>

         <p>3. Coahkkal gilkora <strong>Tastaturmeny</strong> ja merke <strong>Nordsamisk:</strong></p>

         <p><img alt="Lasihit sámi boallobeavddi"
         src="images/enable_sme_keyboard-select_sme-osx10.8-nob.png" /></p>

         <p>4. Dárkkis ahte <strong>Vis tastaturmenyen i
         menylinjen</strong> lea merkejuvvon:</p>

         <p><img alt="Lasihit boallobeavdefálu"
         src="images/enable_sme_keyboard-enable_keyboard_menu-osx10.8-nob.png" /></p>

         <p>5. Vállje de sámi boallobeavddi fálus olgešbealde go áiggut čállit sámegiela:</p>

         <p><img alt="Vállje sámi boallobeavddi čállimii"

         src="images/enable_sme_keyboard-select_sme_input-osx10.8-nob.png" /></p>
      </section>
